estments\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She spoke with journalists on the sidelines of the 4th edition of a two-day mini-table tennis tournament for children from South South and South East regions of Nigeria organised by Offiong Edem Foundation.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.067393183753717e-17, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offiong_Edem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Offiong Edem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offiong_Edem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offiong_Edem\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4th edition\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-day mini-table tennis tournament\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"South South and South East regions\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to her, although she paid a visit to the state Deputy Governor, Peter Odey, to brief him about the mini tournament, the government has not recognized her accomplishments in the game of table tennis.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\", \"score\": 0.9426459866054057, \"rank\": 0.040230642139305425, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19546\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Peter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": 